    "help": {
      "topics": [
        {
          "id": "overview",
          "title": "Summer Themes",
          "content": "# Summer Themes\n\nA collection of five summer-inspired color themes for Clubhouse.\n\n## Themes\n\n### Sunset Beach (Light)\nWarm coral and sandy tones, like watching the sun dip below the ocean from a quiet beach.\n\n### Ocean Breeze (Light)\nCool teals and aquas. A refreshing palette inspired by gentle seaside winds and sparkling water.\n\n### Tropical (Light)\nLush, vivid greens with bold pink hibiscus accents — a walk through a tropical rainforest canopy.\n\n### Golden Hour (Light)\nRich amber and honey tones bathed in the warm glow of late-afternoon sunlight.\n\n### Midnight Swim (Dark)\nDeep ocean blues with luminous teal and coral accents — a warm night swim under the stars.\n\n## Usage\n\nInstall the plugin and select any Summer Theme from **Settings > Appearance > Theme**."
        }
      ]
